  "metaDescription": "Use the SiteFlow Company Dashboard to view project status, sales and expense trends, payment cash flow, expense type breakdown, and project-wise financial summary.",
  "canonical": "https://siteflow.com/help/company-features/how-to-use-the-company-dashboard-in-SiteFlow/",
